Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
Hello
How can I help?
Hello, how can I help?
I am interested in viewing an apartment.
You suddenly remember that you have a job interview on Friday at 11 am. [instruction 2 of 6]
Which apartment?
What apartment are you interested in?
I am so nervous. The job interview is this Friday at 11AM! I will need a place at North Hill ASAP.
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
What's your name?
Could you give me your name, please?
Is the apartment a good one? I've never been there.

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
It has a good reputation.  I hope you like it.
It has a good reputation.  I hope you like it.
Cool! My name is Mark by the way.
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your job interview. [instruction 5 of 6]
What day?
What day would you like to make the booking for?
Friday at 11 works. Oh, but I can't remember if I payed the application fee. Hope you can still book.
When you are done with all the instructions, bring the conversation to a natural close.  [instruction 6 of 6]
I will need that information to schedule the appointment.  Is there any way you could find out if you've already paid the fee?
I will need that information to schedule the appointment.  Is there any way you could find out if you've already paid the fee?
Yes. I remember a pretty person collecting the fee. It is all coming back to me.
Could you confirm the day and time you'd like to book?  You have currently given me the time of your job interview.
Could you confirm the day and time you'd like to book?  You have currently given me the time of your job interview.
Yes. Friday any time before 11AM. This is my first job interview and I do not want to be late.
There is an available time slot at the North Hill Apartments on Friday at 9 am.  Would you like me to book that?
There is an available time slot at the North Hill Apartments on Friday at 9 am.  Would you like me to book that?
Yes. That works great.
